      "title": "Food",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Food\">Food</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Bittercup_Items&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Food\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th>Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\">Weight\n</th>\n<th width=\"22\">Value\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Hunger\" title=\"Skyrim:Hunger\">Hunger</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Survival_Mode\" title=\"Skyrim:Survival Mode\">CC</a></sup>\n</th>\n<th>Effect(s)\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Ingredients\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Ironwood_Soup\">\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-food-Ironwood Soup.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/48px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/72px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/96px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>Ironwood Soup<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">F93</span></span>)</span>\n</td>\n<td>0.5</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Large\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Health\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Health\">Restore Health</a>, 15 pts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Stamina\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Stamina\">Restore Stamina</a>, 15 pts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Cure_Disease\" title=\"Skyrim:Cure Disease\">Cure Disease</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Salt_Pile\" title=\"Skyrim:Salt Pile\">Salt Pile</a><br /><a href=\"#Miscellanous_Items\">Ironwood Fruit</a><br /><a href=\"#Miscellanous_Items\">Charred Skeever Hide</a>\n</td>\n<td>Quest item for <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:A_Dying_Wish\" title=\"Skyrim:A Dying Wish\">A Dying Wish</a>, created with the <a href=\"#Miscellaneous_Items\">miscellaneous items</a> versions of its ingredients.\n</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Ironwood_Soup\">\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-food-Ironwood Soup.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/48px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/72px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/96px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>Ironwood Soup<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">F87</span></span>)</span>\n</td>\n<td>0.5</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Large\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Health\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Health\">Restore Health</a>, 15 pts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Stamina\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Stamina\">Restore Stamina</a>, 15 pts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Cure_Disease\" title=\"Skyrim:Cure Disease\">Cure Disease</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Charred_Skeever_Hide\" title=\"Skyrim:Charred Skeever Hide\">Charred Skeever Hide</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Salt_Pile\" title=\"Skyrim:Salt Pile\">Salt Pile</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ironwood_Fruit\" title=\"Skyrim:Ironwood Fruit\">Ironwood Fruit</a>\n</td>\n<td>Regular version created outside of the quest.\n</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"citation\" id=\"Hot_Ironwood_Soup\">\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-food-Ironwood Soup.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/48px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/72px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/e/ed/SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png/96px-SR-icon-food-Ironwood_Soup.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>Hot Ironwood Soup<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">CE5</span></span>)</span>\n</td>\n<td>0.5</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Large\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Health\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Health\">Restore Health</a>, 15 pts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Stamina\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Stamina\">Restore Stamina</a>, 15 pts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Cure_Disease\" title=\"Skyrim:Cure Disease\">Cure Disease</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fortify_Warmth\" title=\"Skyrim:Fortify Warmth\">Fortify Warmth</a>, 25 pts for 300 secs</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Restore_Cold\" title=\"Skyrim:Restore Cold\">Restore Cold</a>, 200 pts</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Charred_Skeever_Hide\" title=\"Skyrim:Charred Skeever Hide\">Charred Skeever Hide</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fire_Salts\" title=\"Skyrim:Fire Salts\">Fire Salts</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Salt_Pile\" title=\"Skyrim:Salt Pile\">Salt Pile</a><br /><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ironwood_Fruit\" title=\"Skyrim:Ironwood Fruit\">Ironwood Fruit</a>\n</td>\n<td>Only available when <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Survival_Mode\" title=\"Skyrim:Survival Mode\">Survival Mode</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Survival_Mode\" title=\"Skyrim:Survival Mode\">CC</a></sup> is enabled.\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content1.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152108\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.024 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 314/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2022/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 219/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.848      1 -total\n 45.71%    5.873      3 Template:ID\n 25.43%    3.267      3 Template:HE\n 14.38%    1.848      1 Template:Creation_Club\n 13.19%    1.695      1 Template:CC\n-->\n</div>"
